{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable","post":{"title":"区域和检索 - 数组不可变","body":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/range-sum-query-immutable/\">303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这一题非常简单，用前缀和就可以直接撸出来了。举个例子：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>输入数组为 <code>nums = [-2, 0, 3, -5, 2, -1]</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>前缀和为 <code>prefixSum = [-2, -2, 1, -4, -2, -3]</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>那么</p>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>sumRange(0, 2) = prefixSum[2] - prefixSum[0] + nums[0] = 1</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>sumRange(2, 5) = prefixSum[5] - prefixSum[2] + nums[2] = -1</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>代码也超级简单不写了。</p>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"63. 不同路径 II","path":"lc-unique-paths-ii"},{"title":"64. 最小路径和","path":"lc-minimum-path-sum"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}